David Huffman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/David_Huffman 0 David Oliver Huffman (May 10, 1945 – February 27, 1985) was an American stage, television and film actor. His parents are Clarence Huffman a Western Electric shop foreman (retired) and Opal Huffman (née Dippel).
